{"vocabInfos":[{"lsjDefs":"<b> δηλ-όω</b>:—<br /> <i>passive</i>, <i>future</i> δηλωθήσομαι [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Thucydides Historicus 1.144 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; δηλώσομαι in <i>passive</i> sense, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Sophocles Tragicus “Oedipus Coloneus” 581; δεδηλώσομαι 5th c.BC: Hippocrates Medicus “περὶ ἄρθρων ἐμβολῆς” 45, 5th c.BC: Diogenes Apolloniates Philosophus 4 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]:—<b>make visible</b> or <b>manifest, show, exhibit,</b> τὸν ἄνδρ᾽ Ἀχαιοῖς δ. [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Sophocles Tragicus “Philoctetes” 616; ποῖον ὄμμα πατρὶ δηλώσ; [prev. author] “Aj.” 462 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]: with <i>infinitive</i> added, ὡς γένος ἄτλητον ἀνθρώποισι δηλώσοιμ᾽ ὁρᾶν [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] “OT” 792, etc.\">Refs</a>]:—<i>passive</i>, <b>to be</b> or <b>become manifest,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] “OC” 581, etc. \">Refs</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__2</b></Level3> <b>make known, disclose, reveal,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 4th-5th c.BC: Aeschylus Tragicus “Persae” 519, 5th c.BC: Sophocles Tragicus “Oedipus Tyrannus” 77, etc.\">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; <b>prove,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] “OC” 146, 5th c.BC: Thucydides Historicus 1.3; δηλοῖ ὁ λόγος ὅτι.. 3rd c.AD: Democritus Epigrammaticus 7; αὐτὸ δηλώσει 4th c.BC: Demosthenes Orator 19.157 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; <b>explain, set forth,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Thucydides Historicus 2.62 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; <b>signify,</b> ἐδήλουν οὐδὲν ὅτι ἴσασιν <b>gave</b> no <b>sign</b> of knowing, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] 4.68 \">Refs</a>]: <b>indicate,</b> τὰς μεγίστας καὶ ἐλαχίστας [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] 1.10, etc. Construct.: mostly δ. τινί τι 5th c.BC: Antipho Orator 1.30 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; δ. τι πρός or εἴς τινα, [<a href=\"ja